          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">O</hi>N rainy Days alone I dine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-2" n="2">Upon a Chick, and Pint of Wine.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-3" n="3">On rainy Days I dine alone,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-4" n="4">And pick my Chicken to the Bone:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-5" n="5">But this my Servants much enrages,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-6" n="6">No Scraps remain to save Board-wages.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-7" n="7">In Weather fine I nothing spend,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-8" n="8">But often spunge upon a Friend:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-9" n="9">Yet where He's not so rich as I,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-0852-line-10" n="10">I pay my Club, and so G<hi rend="small-caps">OD</hi> b'y'────.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
